WEBVTT

00:00:02.216 --> 00:00:04.320
♪♪

00:00:06.191 --> 00:00:08.128
( humans and goblins
yelling and grunting )

00:00:19.618 --> 00:00:20.553
Goblin: HMM?

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:22.591
♪♪

00:00:25.530 --> 00:00:26.431
( goblins scream )

00:00:26.498 --> 00:00:28.068
Fizel: I CAN’T BELIEVE GOBLINS

00:00:28.135 --> 00:00:30.172
GOT THIS FAR PAST OUR DEFENSES.

00:00:30.239 --> 00:00:33.245
Linel: I KNOW, AND THERE
SEEMS TO BE NO END TO THEM.

00:00:33.311 --> 00:00:35.684
I THINK THERE MIGHT BE
TOO MANY FOR US TO DEAL WITH!

00:00:35.751 --> 00:00:39.057
Fizel: I BET THEY’RE HERE ’CAUSE
RENLICCHI ABANDONED HIS POST.

00:00:39.124 --> 00:00:40.059
( scoffs )

00:00:40.125 --> 00:00:42.129
( goblin yells )

00:00:48.609 --> 00:00:51.749
Linel: HE PROBABLY DID,
THAT COWARD.

00:00:51.816 --> 00:00:54.220
( Renly shudders )

00:02:33.516 --> 00:02:36.755
Renly: I MUST RETURN
TO MY STATION NOW.

00:02:36.822 --> 00:02:38.526
BUT THEN...

00:02:38.593 --> 00:02:43.034
IF I WENT BACK,
I’D JUST BE IN THE WAY.

00:02:43.101 --> 00:02:44.169
Administrator: RENLY.

00:02:46.642 --> 00:02:47.576
Renly: MM?

00:02:47.643 --> 00:02:49.580
♪♪

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:52.218
Administrator: POOR CHILD.

00:02:53.388 --> 00:02:56.127
IT SEEMS THAT YOU ARE BROKEN.

00:02:56.194 --> 00:02:58.098
( Renly gasps )

00:02:58.164 --> 00:03:00.268
BROKEN?

00:03:00.335 --> 00:03:02.372
Chudelkin: YOU ARE A FAILURE!

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.175
( laughs )

00:03:03.241 --> 00:03:05.244
OH, A DEFECTIVE KNIGHT!

00:03:05.311 --> 00:03:07.349
Administrator:
RENLY, I HAVE NO CHOICE,

00:03:07.416 --> 00:03:10.055
BUT TO PUNISH YOU
WITH DEEPFREEZE.

00:03:10.122 --> 00:03:11.357
( Renly gasps )

00:03:11.423 --> 00:03:12.994
Administrator: DESPITE
THE DOUBLE-WINGED BLADES

00:03:13.061 --> 00:03:15.365
CHOOSING YOU AS THEIR MASTER,

00:03:15.432 --> 00:03:17.937
YOU’VE NEVER ACHIEVED PERFECT
WEAPON CONTROL OVER THEM.

00:03:18.004 --> 00:03:22.178
AS A KNIGHT, YOU ARE LACKING
SOMETHING MOST CRUCIAL.

00:03:24.684 --> 00:03:27.122
GOOD NIGHT, RENLY.

00:03:27.189 --> 00:03:29.861
( Chudelkin laughs )
DID YOU HEAR THAT?

00:03:29.927 --> 00:03:31.765
HER EMINENCE
BADE YOU GOOD NIGHT.

00:03:31.832 --> 00:03:33.669
OH, WHAT A LUCKY BOY YOU ARE!

00:03:33.736 --> 00:03:35.037
I’M SO JEALOUS!

00:03:35.104 --> 00:03:37.375
♪♪

00:03:40.716 --> 00:03:42.620
Renly: I AM A FAILURE.

00:03:44.624 --> 00:03:45.893
A FAIL--

00:03:49.132 --> 00:03:50.302
( gasps )

00:03:50.368 --> 00:03:55.212
IT DOES NOT MATTER
WHETHER I EXIST OR NOT.

00:03:55.278 --> 00:03:56.781
Ronie: WHAT ABOUT HERE?

00:03:56.848 --> 00:03:59.621
Tiese: SURE. THIS TENT
LOOKS LIKE IT’LL BE SAFE ENOUGH.

00:03:59.688 --> 00:04:00.421
( Renly gasps )

00:04:01.625 --> 00:04:03.261
Tiese:
WE’LL TUCK HIM AWAY IN BACK

00:04:03.328 --> 00:04:04.964
AND STAND GUARD
AT THE ENTRANCE.

00:04:08.772 --> 00:04:09.707
( Ronie sighs )

00:04:09.774 --> 00:04:11.177
( Renly gasps )

00:04:11.243 --> 00:04:12.279
Tiese: IT’S SO DARK.

00:04:12.346 --> 00:04:13.649
- ( rattle )
- ( gasps )

00:04:13.716 --> 00:04:14.951
IS SOMEONE THERE?

00:04:19.126 --> 00:04:21.097
- Renly: IT IS I.
- ( both gasp )

00:04:21.164 --> 00:04:23.067
Renly: I DID NOT MEAN
TO STARTLE YOU.

00:04:23.134 --> 00:04:25.639
Tiese: UH, SIR KNIGHT!

00:04:25.706 --> 00:04:27.342
- ( Ronie groans )
- Tiese: FORGIVE OUR INTRUSION.

00:04:27.409 --> 00:04:30.749
Renly: NO. I AM AT FAULT HERE.

00:04:30.816 --> 00:04:33.789
AND, PLEASE, BE AT EASE.

00:04:33.856 --> 00:04:35.692
I AM NO LONGER A KNIGHT.

00:04:36.761 --> 00:04:38.131
I AM A DESERTER.

00:04:38.197 --> 00:04:39.634
( both gasp )

00:04:39.701 --> 00:04:41.437
Renly: THE UNIT
I WAS ASSIGNED TO COMMAND

00:04:41.505 --> 00:04:43.743
MUST BE IN A PANIC BY NOW.

00:04:43.809 --> 00:04:46.447
I AM SURE SOME HAVE DIED.

00:04:46.514 --> 00:04:50.989
AND YET I HIDE HERE IN SAFETY
LIKE A FILTHY COWARD.

00:04:54.130 --> 00:04:55.566
Ronie: WHERE ARE MY MANNERS?

00:04:55.633 --> 00:04:58.137
WE HAVEN’T
INTRODUCED OURSELVES YET.

00:04:58.204 --> 00:05:00.776
MY NAME IS RONIE ARABEL.

00:05:00.843 --> 00:05:03.381
THIS IS TIESE SCHTRINEN.

00:05:03.447 --> 00:05:05.017
AND THE ONE BEHIND HER...

00:05:06.688 --> 00:05:09.193
THAT’S ELITE DISCIPLE KIRITO.

00:05:09.259 --> 00:05:11.463
Renly: KIRITO?

00:05:11.531 --> 00:05:14.571
HE IS THE ONE
WHO KILLED THE PONTIFEX?

00:05:14.637 --> 00:05:19.045
Ronie: SIR KNIGHT, FORGIVE ME
IF I’M BEING IMPERTINENT,

00:05:19.112 --> 00:05:22.452
BUT SINCE YOU’RE HERE,
COULD YOU PLEASE HELP US?

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:25.525
WE HATE TO ASK, BUT YOU SEE,

00:05:25.592 --> 00:05:29.299
WE GAVE OUR WORD WE’D KEEP
KIRITO SAFE, NO MATTER WHAT.

00:05:29.366 --> 00:05:31.103
( Renly gasps )

00:05:31.170 --> 00:05:33.107
Ronie: WE’RE STILL
PRIMARY TRAINEES.

00:05:33.174 --> 00:05:36.681
WE CAN’T DEFEND OURSELVES
AGAINST THINGS LIKE GOBLINS YET.

00:05:36.748 --> 00:05:40.790
EVEN SO, WE ACCEPTED
THIS RESPONSIBILITY.

00:05:40.856 --> 00:05:42.660
WE HAVE TO KEEP HIM SAFE.

00:05:42.726 --> 00:05:45.064
LADY ALICE IS COUNTING ON US TO.

00:05:47.604 --> 00:05:48.539
- ( man yells )
- ( body thumps )

00:05:48.605 --> 00:05:50.441
- ( all gasp )
- Tiese: OH, NO!

00:05:50.509 --> 00:05:52.379
THE ENEMY’S ALREADY HERE.

00:05:52.446 --> 00:05:53.715
- ( goblin growls )
- ( man screams )

00:05:53.782 --> 00:05:55.418
( man gags )

00:05:55.485 --> 00:05:57.422
- Tiese: I SEE SMOKE.
- Ronie: WHAT?

00:05:57.489 --> 00:05:59.661
A-ARE THEY SETTING
THE TENTS ON FIRE?

00:05:59.728 --> 00:06:01.431
- ( men groaning, yelling )
- Tiese: THERE’S NO FIRE,

00:06:01.497 --> 00:06:04.269
JUST A WHOLE LOT
OF THIS WEIRD-LOOKING SMOKE.

00:06:04.336 --> 00:06:08.178
WAIT. NOW I CAN SEE SHAPES
MOVING AROUND IN IT.

00:06:08.244 --> 00:06:09.212
( gasps )

00:06:09.279 --> 00:06:11.450
♪♪

00:06:11.518 --> 00:06:12.887
( Ronie whimpers )

00:06:21.805 --> 00:06:22.740
( goblin growls )

00:06:22.806 --> 00:06:24.309
Ronie: A GOBLIN!

00:06:24.376 --> 00:06:26.180
- ( Renly gasps )
- Goblin: LOOKY HERE!

00:06:26.247 --> 00:06:29.486
I FOUND ME
SOME WHITE IUM GIRLIES.

00:06:29.554 --> 00:06:31.791
( laughs ) WHAT A LUCKY DAY.

00:06:35.431 --> 00:06:37.570
Ronie: TIESE.

00:06:37.637 --> 00:06:40.074
- ( goblin chuckles )
- ( girls shuddering )

00:06:45.519 --> 00:06:47.455
( Renly gasping )

00:06:54.570 --> 00:06:58.278
Swordsman: I’M GOING TO WIN
THE TOURNAMENT TODAY, RENLY!

00:06:58.344 --> 00:06:59.479
Renly: NO, I AM!

00:06:59.547 --> 00:07:01.483
♪♪

00:07:05.458 --> 00:07:06.393
[metal clinks]

00:07:08.364 --> 00:07:09.934
TOO SLOW!

00:07:15.679 --> 00:07:18.117
( gasps )

00:07:18.184 --> 00:07:20.589
( swordsman gasps )

00:07:21.658 --> 00:07:23.595
♪♪

00:07:28.471 --> 00:07:30.408
( Renly gasping )

00:07:32.446 --> 00:07:35.519
( swordsman gasps ) RENLY...

00:07:40.495 --> 00:07:42.198
Tiese: S-STAY BACK!

00:07:42.265 --> 00:07:43.267
I-I’M WARNING YOU!

00:07:43.334 --> 00:07:44.370
( goblin slurps )

00:07:44.437 --> 00:07:46.340
SO FEISTY. SO TASTY!

00:07:46.407 --> 00:07:49.079
Tiese: IF YOU COME ANY CLOSER,
I’LL KILL YOU!

00:07:50.348 --> 00:07:51.450
( fist creaking )

00:07:51.518 --> 00:07:52.452
( Renly gasps )

00:07:55.057 --> 00:07:56.828
♪♪

00:08:03.107 --> 00:08:05.211
ARE YOU--

00:08:05.278 --> 00:08:07.115
ARE YOU TRYING
TO PROTECT THESE TWO?

00:08:08.384 --> 00:08:09.821
YOU STRUGGLE TO,

00:08:09.888 --> 00:08:15.065
EVEN THOUGH YOU CANNOT STAND
OR SPEAK OR DRAW YOUR SWORD,

00:08:15.131 --> 00:08:18.103
WHILE I COWER.

00:08:20.441 --> 00:08:21.577
( sword clangs )

00:08:26.622 --> 00:08:27.389
Swordsman: RENLY...

00:08:27.455 --> 00:08:29.527
( shuddering )

00:08:30.394 --> 00:08:32.534
I WANT YOU...

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:34.670
TO BECOME A GREAT KNIGHT.

00:08:36.339 --> 00:08:38.010
DO IT FOR ME.

00:08:48.130 --> 00:08:49.399
( gasps )

00:08:49.466 --> 00:08:51.136
( grunts )

00:08:53.575 --> 00:08:55.177
- ( goblin growls )
- ( girls gasp )

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:04.697
( goblin gasping )

00:09:09.272 --> 00:09:10.809
( sword clangs )

00:09:10.876 --> 00:09:11.911
Both: HUH?

00:09:13.116 --> 00:09:14.451
( Renly panting )

00:09:14.519 --> 00:09:15.622
Tiese: SIR KNIGHT!

00:09:15.688 --> 00:09:18.492
YOU DID IT! YOU SAVED US!

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.129
THANK YOU SO MUCH!

00:09:29.214 --> 00:09:31.452
( Renly breathes deeply )

00:09:31.520 --> 00:09:33.423
STAY HERE, PLEASE,

00:09:33.490 --> 00:09:34.659
AND PROTECT KIRITO.

00:09:34.726 --> 00:09:36.195
Both: Y-YES, SIR.

00:09:37.297 --> 00:09:39.602
♪♪

00:09:40.470 --> 00:09:41.606
Goblins: EH?

00:09:42.642 --> 00:09:45.079
( goblins growling )

00:09:45.146 --> 00:09:46.617
Renly: I AM RENLY,

00:09:46.683 --> 00:09:50.558
INTEGRITY KNIGHT
RENLY SYNTHESIS TWENTY-SEVEN!

00:09:50.625 --> 00:09:51.960
IF YOU WANT MY HEAD,

00:09:52.028 --> 00:09:54.166
THEN BE READY
TO GIVE YOUR LIVES FOR IT!

00:09:54.233 --> 00:09:55.868
Goblin: CHOP HIM TO PIECES!

00:09:55.935 --> 00:09:59.009
( goblin 2 roars )

00:09:59.076 --> 00:10:00.778
( goblins shriek )

00:10:06.690 --> 00:10:08.127
Renly: I CAN DO THIS.

00:10:08.193 --> 00:10:10.499
BY NOW, THE SMOKE SHOULD BE
CLEARING FROM THE FRONT LINES.

00:10:10.565 --> 00:10:12.936
ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS HOLD OUT A LITTLE LONGER,

00:10:13.004 --> 00:10:13.771
AND HELP WILL ARRIVE.

00:10:16.176 --> 00:10:17.612
( metal clangs )

00:10:19.883 --> 00:10:21.019
( gasps )

00:10:21.086 --> 00:10:22.655
( footsteps thudding )

00:10:22.722 --> 00:10:24.993
♪♪

00:10:25.061 --> 00:10:27.732
( Kosogi chuckles )

00:10:29.203 --> 00:10:30.738
Renly: ARE YOU THEIR COMMANDER?

00:10:30.805 --> 00:10:33.077
Kosogi: YEAH. I BE KOSOGI,

00:10:33.144 --> 00:10:35.715
CHIEF OF THE MOUNTAIN GOBLINS.

00:10:35.781 --> 00:10:37.285
WHAT A SHAME.

00:10:37.352 --> 00:10:39.923
YOU DONE KILLED
SOME OF MY BEST WARRIORS.

00:10:39.990 --> 00:10:42.329
SURPRISED TO FIND YE HERE...

00:10:42.396 --> 00:10:45.067
YE BEIN’ AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT
AND ALL.

00:10:45.134 --> 00:10:47.139
WHY AIN’T YOU BE
WHERE THE ACTION IS,

00:10:47.205 --> 00:10:48.273
WITH THE OTHER KNIGHTS?

00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:50.745
Renly: THAT IS
NONE OF YOUR CONCERN.

00:10:50.812 --> 00:10:51.647
NOW PERISH!

00:10:53.985 --> 00:10:54.786
( Kosogi chuckles )

00:10:54.853 --> 00:10:56.090
( grunts )

00:10:56.157 --> 00:10:57.825
( Renly gasps )

00:11:02.735 --> 00:11:06.276
Kosogi: THOUGHT I WAS JUST
ANOTHER GOBLIN, DID YE, BOY?

00:11:06.343 --> 00:11:09.916
WELL, I AIN’T SO IMPRESSED
WITH YE, EITHER, TO BE HONEST.

00:11:11.486 --> 00:11:14.226
YOU SAID BEFORE
YOU WERE AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT.

00:11:14.292 --> 00:11:17.732
I WAS TOLD ONE OF YOU
COULD TAKE ON A THOUSAND.

00:11:17.799 --> 00:11:21.607
BUT THAT AIN’T THE CASE
FOR YE, NOW, IS IT? ( chuckles )

00:11:21.673 --> 00:11:25.782
THAT’S WHY YE BE HIDIN’
ALL THE WAY BACK HERE.

00:11:25.849 --> 00:11:27.552
AIN’T THAT RIGHT?

00:11:27.619 --> 00:11:31.159
Administrator: IT SEEMS
THAT YOU ARE BROKEN, CHILD.

00:11:31.226 --> 00:11:33.030
Renly: PERHAPS SHE WAS RIGHT.

00:11:33.097 --> 00:11:34.966
I AM A FAILURE.

00:11:35.034 --> 00:11:36.736
MAYBE I AM.

00:11:36.803 --> 00:11:38.707
♪♪

00:11:38.774 --> 00:11:41.046
( chuckles ) YOU ARE CORRECT.

00:11:41.113 --> 00:11:43.117
I AM NOT MUCH OF A KNIGHT.

00:11:43.183 --> 00:11:46.056
EVEN SO, LET US BE CLEAR.

00:11:46.123 --> 00:11:48.661
THOUGH I MIGHT BE DEFECTIVE,

00:11:48.727 --> 00:11:49.596
THESE ARE NOT!

00:11:50.865 --> 00:11:53.337
♪♪

00:12:04.726 --> 00:12:05.728
( Kosogi gasps )

00:12:07.331 --> 00:12:10.504
Renly: DOUBLE WINGS,
TAKE FLIGHT!

00:12:12.108 --> 00:12:13.777
( Kosogi growls )

00:12:13.844 --> 00:12:16.150
I CAN DO THIS ALL DAY, BOY!

00:12:16.217 --> 00:12:17.852
Renly: RELEASE...

00:12:18.921 --> 00:12:19.856
RECOLLECTION!

00:12:28.841 --> 00:12:29.943
BEAUTIFUL.

00:12:37.024 --> 00:12:40.965
Kosogi: QUIT PLAYIN’ AROUND!

00:12:44.939 --> 00:12:47.378
( roars )

00:12:54.192 --> 00:12:55.728
( gags )

00:13:06.216 --> 00:13:08.620
- Fizel: RENLICCHI?
- Renly: EH?

00:13:08.687 --> 00:13:10.357
♪♪

00:13:11.660 --> 00:13:12.395
( stammers )

00:13:12.462 --> 00:13:14.266
Fizel: WELL, WELL, WELL.

00:13:14.333 --> 00:13:16.770
SOMEONE’S GOTTEN
A BIT MORE KNIGHTLY.

00:13:16.837 --> 00:13:19.843
WE WERE HOPING
TO GET CREDIT FOR SAVING YOU.

00:13:19.910 --> 00:13:21.647
TOO BAD YOU HAD TO SPOIL THAT.

00:13:21.714 --> 00:13:23.617
( Linel sighs )
NO ONE’S GONNA CARE

00:13:23.684 --> 00:13:25.722
THAT WE CHOPPED OFF
WAY MORE HEADS THAN YOU DID.

00:13:25.788 --> 00:13:26.523
( Fizel groans )

00:13:28.594 --> 00:13:32.135
Both: SIR KNIGHT,
WE HUMBLY REQUEST YOUR ORDERS.

00:13:32.202 --> 00:13:34.072
( Renly gasps )

00:13:34.139 --> 00:13:35.942
( clears throat )

00:13:36.009 --> 00:13:37.312
VERY WELL, THEN.

00:13:37.379 --> 00:13:39.650
KEEP KIRITO AND THE GIRLS SAFE.

00:13:39.716 --> 00:13:41.554
Fizel: YOU DON’T
HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT THAT.

00:13:41.620 --> 00:13:44.192
WE HANDED THEM ALL OFF
TO THE SUPPLY CORPS JUST NOW.

00:13:44.259 --> 00:13:46.297
( Renly sighs )

00:13:46.363 --> 00:13:48.067
WE SHOULD SECURE THE AREA, THEN.

00:13:48.134 --> 00:13:49.669
Linel: WE KILLED
ALL THE GOBLINS HERE.

00:13:49.736 --> 00:13:50.471
( Renly gasps )

00:13:50.538 --> 00:13:52.242
I-IF THAT IS THE CASE,

00:13:52.309 --> 00:13:54.947
THEN I SUPPOSE
WE’D BEST RETURN TO OUR UNITS.

00:13:55.014 --> 00:13:56.083
Fizel: YES, SIR.

00:13:56.150 --> 00:13:57.485
Linel: AS YOU COMMAND.

00:14:06.270 --> 00:14:07.471
Renly: THANK YOU.

00:14:17.427 --> 00:14:20.968
Mage: LORD SIGUROSIG,
LORD SHIBORI, AND LORD KOSOGI

00:14:21.035 --> 00:14:22.471
HAVE ALL BEEN KILLED.

00:14:22.539 --> 00:14:24.408
Dee: USELESS WRETCHES.

00:14:24.475 --> 00:14:27.148
DEMI-HUMANS CAN’T BE
COUNTED ON FOR ANYTHING.

00:14:27.214 --> 00:14:30.855
HAVE YOU LOCATED
ALL THE INTEGRITY KNIGHTS YET?

00:14:30.922 --> 00:14:32.559
Mage: CURRENTLY
WE HAVE THE THREE

00:14:32.625 --> 00:14:34.295
ON THE FRONT LINES
IN OUR SIGHTS.

00:14:34.362 --> 00:14:37.067
WE FOUND TWO MORE
AMONG THEIR REAR UNITS,

00:14:37.134 --> 00:14:39.338
BUT WE DO NOT
HAVE A FIX ON THEM YET.

00:14:39.405 --> 00:14:42.044
Dee: THERE ARE
ONLY FIVE KNIGHTS HERE?

00:14:42.111 --> 00:14:45.284
IMPOSSIBLE, UNLESS THAT IS
ALL THEY EVER HAD.

00:14:45.351 --> 00:14:48.022
REGARDLESS OF HOW MANY
THERE ARE HERE,

00:14:48.089 --> 00:14:50.561
WE MUST SLAUGHTER THEM ALL.

00:14:50.628 --> 00:14:52.599
GO ON. WAKE THE MINIONS.

00:14:52.666 --> 00:14:54.702
HAVE THEM FLY FOR 700 MELS,

00:14:54.769 --> 00:14:57.174
THEN DESCEND
UPON THE BATTLEFIELD...

00:14:58.043 --> 00:15:00.013
AND KILL EVERYTHING.

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.449
Mage: FORGIVE THE QUESTION,

00:15:01.517 --> 00:15:04.188
BUT WON’T OUR DEMI-HUMAN UNITS
GET CAUGHT IN THAT?

00:15:04.254 --> 00:15:05.791
- Dee: TOO BAD.
- Mage: RIGHT.

00:15:05.858 --> 00:15:08.664
HOW MANY MINIONS DO YOU WISH?

00:15:08.731 --> 00:15:10.735
WE HAVE 800 AVAILABLE.

00:15:10.802 --> 00:15:12.506
THEY ARE ALL
HATCHED AND READY TO GO.

00:15:12.572 --> 00:15:14.208
Dee: HMM.

00:15:16.279 --> 00:15:17.147
( slurps )

00:15:18.216 --> 00:15:20.353
SEND EVERY LAST ONE OF THEM.

00:15:23.560 --> 00:15:26.132
( minion roars )

00:15:29.204 --> 00:15:30.708
Bercouli: HERE THEY COME.

00:15:30.775 --> 00:15:32.912
♪♪

00:15:59.031 --> 00:16:01.402
TIME-SPLITTING SWORD!

00:16:01.469 --> 00:16:03.339
( chorus vocalizing )

00:16:03.406 --> 00:16:04.308
AIR SLICE!

00:16:06.547 --> 00:16:07.280
( growls )

00:16:26.386 --> 00:16:30.628
Alice: UNCLE ACTIVATED
HIS PERFECT WEAPON CONTROL.

00:16:30.695 --> 00:16:33.299
HE HAS MADE HIS MOVE.

00:16:33.366 --> 00:16:35.003
♪♪

00:16:43.787 --> 00:16:45.123
( no audible dialogue )

00:16:46.593 --> 00:16:47.963
Dee: YOU IMBECILE!

00:16:48.030 --> 00:16:49.766
HOW DID WE NOT KNOW

00:16:49.833 --> 00:16:51.903
THEY HAD
SUCH A LARGE UNIT OF MAGES?

00:16:51.970 --> 00:16:53.975
- Mage: TH-THEY DON’T.
- ( Dee sputtering )

00:16:54.042 --> 00:16:56.111
Mage: I-I DON’T KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED.

00:16:57.749 --> 00:16:59.953
( Dee breathes deeply )

00:17:00.019 --> 00:17:02.425
HAVE THEY DEPLOYED
THEIR FLYING DRAGONS YET?

00:17:02.491 --> 00:17:03.861
Mage: NO.

00:17:03.928 --> 00:17:06.132
THE SKIES ABOVE THE BATTLEFIELD
ARE CLEAR.

00:17:06.198 --> 00:17:08.538
NOT ONE DRAGON HAS BEEN SPOTTED.

00:17:08.604 --> 00:17:12.310
Dee: THEN THERE CAN BE
ONLY ONE EXPLANATION FOR IT.

00:17:12.377 --> 00:17:16.052
THAT MUST BE
PERFECT WEAPON CONTROL,

00:17:16.118 --> 00:17:18.423
THEIR KNIGHT’S SPECIAL SKILL.

00:17:18.490 --> 00:17:19.492
DAMN THEM.

00:17:19.559 --> 00:17:22.364
( scoffs ) THEY ARE
STRONGER THAN I THOUGHT.

00:17:22.431 --> 00:17:26.238
USING A WEAPON THAT WAY
IS RISKY, THOUGH.

00:17:26.305 --> 00:17:28.844
IT WOULD DRAIN MASSIVE AMOUNTS
OF THE KNIGHT’S LIFE.

00:17:28.911 --> 00:17:31.015
HOW COULD THEY UNLEASH
SUCH A BARRAGE?

00:17:31.082 --> 00:17:32.418
Mage: I JUST GOT WORD, MILADY.

00:17:32.485 --> 00:17:35.224
OUR SPOTTERS LOCATED
THE TWO KNIGHTS IN THE REAR.

00:17:35.290 --> 00:17:36.492
WE’VE TARGETED THEM.

00:17:36.560 --> 00:17:39.131
WE NOW HAVE ALL FIVE OF THEM
IN OUR SIGHTS.

00:17:40.568 --> 00:17:41.536
Dee: GOOD.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:45.678
I HAVE WAITED FOR THIS.

00:17:45.744 --> 00:17:50.053
IT IS MY CHANCE FOR GLORY,
AND I SHALL SEIZE IT.

00:17:51.422 --> 00:17:53.026
( sighs )

00:17:53.093 --> 00:17:54.662
OGRE ARCHERS AND DARK MAGES,

00:17:54.729 --> 00:17:56.700
ADVANCE INTO THE RAVINE!

00:17:56.766 --> 00:17:58.202
ONCE YOU ARE IN POSITION,

00:17:58.269 --> 00:18:03.179
READY THE BOWS, AND BEGIN
THE INCINERATION INCANTATION!

00:18:03.246 --> 00:18:04.716
♪♪

00:18:19.746 --> 00:18:21.216
Arch Mage: MAGE UNIT...

00:18:21.282 --> 00:18:25.189
PREPARE FOR WIDE-RANGE
INCINERATION PROJECTILES!

00:18:25.256 --> 00:18:28.295
SPOTTERS, BEGIN THE INCANTATION
TO GUIDE THE PROJECTILES

00:18:28.362 --> 00:18:29.866
TO THE INTEGRITY KNIGHT’S
POSITION!

00:18:31.135 --> 00:18:33.406
OGRES, PREPARE TO FIRE!

00:18:36.278 --> 00:18:38.584
♪♪

00:18:38.617 --> 00:18:40.386
( soldier gags )

00:18:40.453 --> 00:18:41.823
♪♪

00:18:43.728 --> 00:18:46.198
( soldier 2 groans )

00:18:50.608 --> 00:18:51.977
Alice: WHY IS IT...

00:18:52.044 --> 00:18:55.016
THAT THE SOULS
OF THE FALLEN BELOW,

00:18:55.083 --> 00:18:57.321
WHETHER HUMAN OR DEMI-HUMAN,

00:18:57.387 --> 00:19:00.861
GENERATE SACRED POWER
THAT IS SO WARM AND PURE?

00:19:02.431 --> 00:19:04.502
THE PEOPLE OF THE HUMAN EMPIRE

00:19:04.569 --> 00:19:06.372
AND THE MONSTERS
OF THE DARK TERRITORY

00:19:06.438 --> 00:19:09.612
HAVE ESSENTIALLY THE SAME SOULS.

00:19:11.182 --> 00:19:13.186
THE ONLY DIFFERENCE
IS WHETHER THEY WERE BORN

00:19:13.253 --> 00:19:16.526
ON ONE SIDE OF THE END MOUNTAINS
OR THE OTHER.

00:19:17.696 --> 00:19:20.233
IF SO, THEN WHY ARE THEY--

00:19:20.300 --> 00:19:22.404
WHY ARE WE FIGHTING?

00:19:24.441 --> 00:19:27.848
KIRITO, IF YOU WERE HERE...

00:19:30.521 --> 00:19:33.661
NO. I RAISED MY SWORD
AGAINST THE PONTIFEX

00:19:33.728 --> 00:19:36.198
AND DEFIED THE AXIOM CHURCH.

00:19:36.265 --> 00:19:39.137
IT IS MY DUTY
TO SEE THIS THROUGH NOW.

00:19:39.204 --> 00:19:40.507
( Amayori trills )

00:19:40.574 --> 00:19:42.311
♪♪

00:19:42.377 --> 00:19:43.312
Alice: THEY’RE HERE.

00:19:44.415 --> 00:19:46.351
AS FAR AS MAINTAINING ELEMENTS,

00:19:46.418 --> 00:19:50.327
I AM NO MATCH FOR WHAT THOUSANDS
OF DARK MAGES ARE CAPABLE OF,

00:19:50.393 --> 00:19:53.834
AND CONVERTING SACRED POWER
INTO FIRE OR ICE ELEMENTS

00:19:53.900 --> 00:19:55.571
WOULD NOT BE
A POTENT ENOUGH ART

00:19:55.638 --> 00:19:59.411
TO SAP ALL THE SPATIAL RESOURCES
RISING FROM THE RAVINE.

00:19:59.478 --> 00:20:01.784
HOWEVER...

00:20:01.817 --> 00:20:04.321
SEALING LUMINOUS ELEMENTS
INSIDE A MIRROR

00:20:04.388 --> 00:20:06.358
WOULD REFLECT THEM INFINITELY,

00:20:12.204 --> 00:20:13.708
Mages: SYSTEM CALL!

00:20:13.774 --> 00:20:15.677
GENERATE THERMAL ELEMENT!

00:20:22.625 --> 00:20:25.330
( mages gasping )

00:20:25.397 --> 00:20:27.333
( Arch Mage gasping )

00:20:28.737 --> 00:20:32.578
SYSTEM CALL!
GENERATE THERMAL ELEMENT!

00:20:33.814 --> 00:20:35.317
( gasps )

00:20:35.384 --> 00:20:38.055
Mage: IT’S NOT WORKING.
WHAT’S GOING ON?

00:20:38.122 --> 00:20:40.327
Mage 2: WHAT’LL WE DO? WE CAN’T
ACTIVATE THE PROJECTILES

00:20:40.393 --> 00:20:42.364
WITHOUT THERMAL ELEMENTS!

00:20:42.430 --> 00:20:45.170
Arch Mage: DAMN! WHY ISN’T
THE INCANTATION WORKING?

00:20:45.237 --> 00:20:46.673
Mage 3: ARCH MAGE, IF I MAY,

00:20:46.740 --> 00:20:50.046
I THINK ALL THE SPATIAL
RESOURCES HAVE BEEN DEPLETED.

00:20:50.113 --> 00:20:52.184
Arch Mage: WHAT?!
ARE YOU INSANE?!

00:20:52.250 --> 00:20:54.522
THAT’S IMPOSSIBLE!
WHAT ABOUT ALL THE SCREAMING?

00:20:54.589 --> 00:20:57.528
SCORES OF BOTH HUMANS AND
DEMI-HUMANS HAVE DIED ALREADY!

00:20:57.595 --> 00:21:01.301
IF THOSE RESOURCES AREN’T HERE,
THEN WHERE DID THEY ALL GO?!

00:21:04.341 --> 00:21:06.479
Alice: THE BURDEN
OF TAKING COUNTLESS LIVES

00:21:06.546 --> 00:21:10.286
FOR THE SAKE OF ONE
SHALL BE MINE TO BEAR.

00:21:13.126 --> 00:21:15.029
BLOOM, FLOWERS!

00:21:15.096 --> 00:21:17.033
( chorus vocalizing )

00:21:32.832 --> 00:21:34.301
( inhales )

00:21:34.367 --> 00:21:36.271
BURST ELEMENT.

00:21:58.283 --> 00:22:00.019
( lava bubbling )